Title: Titan Trash or Titan Treasure?
Description:
The watchers left all sorts of amazing technology just laying around when they went to sleep.

We could learn so much from their ancient castoffs. Even the least of contraptions are marvels to behold!

If only there was someone brave, intelligent, and dare I say handsome enough to go retrieve a few examples for our finest niffeneers back in Loamm to examine... sound familiar?
ObjectivesCompletionText: Deliver the supplies to Scrybbil in Loamm.
